headline.main: BRITISH WILL GET TRANSPORT PLANES; 200 Commercial and Private Craft Are Being Rushed to Combat Nazis in Near East

lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON, May 1 -- President Roosevelt was notified today by Secretary Jones that a substantial number of commercial and privately owned transport planes would be delivered to the government "within three days" for transfer to anti-Axis forces.
abstract: U S commercial and private transport planes requisitioned to meet Nazi onslaughts in Near East
